---
title: Easy Chimichurri Chicken, Chorizo & Veggie Couscous with Tahini & Garlic Sauce
description: Sunset roast veggies, chorizo and chicken seasoned with chimichurri is a colourful combination of flavours. Dollop over a cooling serve of tahini garlic dip to finish off the dish. At the end of the rainbow is a reward of a beautiful veggie couscous topped with mouth-watering chicken.
